<view class="login-page">
  <view class="logo-wrap">
    <image class="logo-img" src="/images/icons/login-logo.svg" mode="aspectFit" />
    <text class="logo-name">秦皇岛野生动物园</text>
    <text class="logo-sub">AI 智能导览</text>
  </view>

  <view class="dev-box">
    <view class="dev-title">接口地址（真机必改）</view>
    <input
      class="dev-input"
      placeholder="只填根地址，如 http://192.168.1.5:8000（不要带/health）"
      value="{{apiBaseInput}}"
      bindinput="onApiBaseInput"
    />
    <view class="dev-row">
      <button class="dev-btn" size="mini" bindtap="saveApiBase">保存地址</button>
      <button class="dev-btn" size="mini" bindtap="resetApiBase">恢复本机默认</button>
      <button class="dev-btn primary" size="mini" bindtap="pingBackend">测试连接</button>
    </view>
    <text class="dev-hint">开发者工具模拟器连本机后端：请用 http://127.0.0.1:8000（勿填已失效的局域网 IP）。云服务器：填 http://公网IP:8000。真机预览：填电脑 ipconfig 的 IPv4 + 同一 WiFi。若提示域名：详情→本地设置→勾选不校验合法域名。后端需 uvicorn main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000</text>
  </view>

  <button class="btn-primary login-btn" hover-class="btn-primary-hover" bindtap="wxLogin">
    微信快捷登录
  </button>
  <view class="tip">微信快捷登录，无需注册</view>
</view>
